genresAdvancedInfo.name: baltic classical piano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This subgenre of Baltic classical music focuses on the piano as the primary instrument. Featuring virtuosic performances and complex compositions, Baltic classical piano music is known for its technical precision and emotional intensity. From delicate ballads to thunderous concertos, this genre showcases the mastery of Baltic pianists and their ability to convey deep emotions through music.
